Set like a jewel on top of Huckleberry Mountain, The French Manor provides an atmosphere for elegant, yet comfortable gatherings, the perfect setting for small exclusive conferences. Our service and gourmet French cuisine is exceptional. The French Manor is an authentic French Chateau, built by Joseph Hirshhorn as a replica of his chateau in France. It is truly a miniature castle. The mountainous setting of the French Manor with magnificent vistas, a stone terrace, and rolling lawns creates a perfect atmosphere for clear productive thinking. The French Manor has nineteen luxurious accommodations and meeting facilities that can accommodate numerous setups. The attentive service of our staff provides an excellent atmosphere for exclusive meetings and banquets.
